### 2.2 Data Cleaning

#### Missing Values Before Cleaning
| Column | Missing |
|---|---|
| age | 392 |
| steps | 439 |
| calories | 457 |
| workout | 436 |

#### Strategies Applied
| Column | Strategy | Reasoning |
|---|---|---|
| age | fillna(median) | Numerical — median preserves distribution |
| steps | fillna(median) | Numerical — median robust to outliers |
| calories | fillna(median) | Numerical — median robust to outliers |
| workout | fillna(mode) | Categorical — most frequent value |
| outliers | Z-score > 3 removed | 235 extreme steps values removed |

#### After Cleaning
- 0 missing values across all columns ✅
- Rows before : 8 926 → Rows after : 8 691
- 235 outlier rows removed (steps > 3 std from mean)

